sentences: Marié Christina Digby ( MAR-ee-AY; born April 16, 1983) is an American singer, songwriter, guitarist and pianist known for her acoustic cover version of Rihanna's "Umbrella", which was posted on YouTube in 2007 (and has since been viewed over 22 million times).

Marié Christina Digby ( MAR-ee-AY; born April 16, 1983) is an American singer, songwriter, guitarist and pianist known for her acoustic cover version of Rihanna's "Umbrella", which was posted on YouTube in 2007 (and has since been viewed over 22 million times).
Digby performed the song on the late night talk show Last Call with Carson Daly on August 2, 2007.
Her fifth studio album Winter Fields was released on October 29, 2013.
On August 16, 2014, Marié released Chimera, a 3 track EP.
